{"id": 1619, "genre": 1001, "title": "你有哪些不堪回首的坐飞机体验？", "description": "Twitter热议美联航乘客被拖下飞机……你也有糟糕可怕的坐飞机体验吗？", "record_count": 3720, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170411102036lxdXOfUVwa8M40Rn.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-11T03:01:29Z", "options": [{"id": 190464, "content": "留学回国，行李寄丢，后来啥也没找回来", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 196609, "content": "刚吃完机上晚餐就开始降落并伴有不稳定气流", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014787}, {"id": 190721, "content": "凌晨抵达目的地，等行李等了一个多小时，出了飞机场，天亮了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417148}, {"id": 190722, "content": "从三亚回来，飞机上全是带小孩的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875232}, {"id": 190979, "content": "座位附近有吵闹的小孩子，家长还不管！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883142}, {"id": 192259, "content": "第一次坐飞机 耳朵嗡嗡作响 一度疼痛难忍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672156}, {"id": 192771, "content": "耳朵疼，从起飞后一直疼到降落，可怕的经历。虽然别的航班也疼过，但没那次那么严重的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863495}, {"id": 190724, "content": "唔，我有恐高症，没坐过飞机。飞机给我的感觉是好高好可怕！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001081}, {"id": 190726, "content": "买的经停那种，有起飞，但是没有到我的目的地，因为台风。?然后最快改签到三天后。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360252}, {"id": 190983, "content": "晕机，坐一次难过半个月?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002355}, {"id": 190728, "content": "往返都因天气原因迫降其他机场", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001810}, {"id": 191752, "content": "还没坐过飞机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403578}, {"id": 194056, "content": "飞机跑道上升的那几秒钟前列腺好激动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008485}, {"id": 190730, "content": "后面的小孩，狂踹我的椅背", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898827}, {"id": 192522, "content": "第一次坐飞机，问空姐要的热水撒了一身", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801363}, {"id": 190476, "content": "延误待定", "image": null, "praise_count": 371, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674815}, {"id": 190732, "content": "10个小时的航班要了两次水被空城说我事多", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136351}, {"id": 193036, "content": "以交通管制为由困在飞机上2个小时不起飞，闷的透不过气来！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930069}, {"id": 190477, "content": "延误待定", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674815}, {"id": 190989, "content": "航空管制，飞机延误几个小时不能按时起飞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993552}, {"id": 191502, "content": "没坐过。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1000657}, {"id": 191758, "content": "几乎每次坐南航都会延误超长时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 757846}, {"id": 193038, "content": "还没做过飞机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260415}, {"id": 190479, "content": "只要舱内有婴儿或者大吼大叫的毛孩，就是不堪回首定体验。", "image": null, "praise_count": 804, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879838}, {"id": 190735, "content": "香港快运 服务态度差得实属一流", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915717}, {"id": 190481, "content": "名字写错，同音字少了一个偏旁，机票就要重买", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 398106}, {"id": 190738, "content": "飞机延误 发了个微博吐槽 然后微博被删了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001871}, {"id": 190994, "content": "出差回家机场等了6个小时后告诉我取消了，给了三百，酒店都是自己找的单人间没了，花了四百五定了个双人间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746895}, {"id": 199444, "content": "一直被滞留在机场！从晚上6点等到凌晨2点，深圳机场！记忆犹新呀！能不能守时！航空管制！飞机老晚点为何？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021133}, {"id": 190486, "content": "变登机口！我有次去北京，1个小时之内换了4次登机口！", "image": null, "praise_count": 113, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893759}, {"id": 190742, "content": "旁边有小孩子而且很多手多脚很吵很闹的那种...戴着耳机都没用的那种...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935602}, {"id": 195606, "content": "国航的飞行员是不是开过战斗机？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1012736}, {"id": 190487, "content": "有婴儿狂哭?‍♂️", "image": null, "praise_count": 169, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771698}, {"id": 194072, "content": "夜间联航 没有座位 嗯 站了一夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962364}, {"id": 190489, "content": "坐过俄航，感觉飞机随时会散架", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787451}, {"id": 191513, "content": "旁边坐着一个满身异味的大妈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686544}, {"id": 190747, "content": "在目的地上空一直盘旋就是不下去，原因是雪太大，差点返回??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 768422}, {"id": 192283, "content": "飞机进入下滑道时候后座的sb拿出手机开机咔咔咔拍照", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004005}, {"id": 190492, "content": "天气问题直接取消并无赔偿", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 96253}, {"id": 190748, "content": "第一次做的时候，有很多飞机上的规矩不太清楚导致出了点小小的差错，也都还好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001915}, {"id": 192028, "content": "就一次坐头等舱，走vip通道，他让我脱鞋检查", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962173}, {"id": 190493, "content": "延误到地老天荒", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 885464}, {"id": 190749, "content": "至今从未做过飞机✈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131379}, {"id": 192285, "content": "飞机餐真的真的真的很难吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978659}, {"id": 190494, "content": "坐在旁边的大哥以上飞机就开始睡觉，呼噜响了一路，降落的时候猛然惊醒，堪比人体闹钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001264}, {"id": 190750, "content": "一遍一遍的听机场广播说你乘坐的xxx由于航空管制暂不能起飞请等待通知", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995844}, {"id": 190495, "content": "托运行李箱破损", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839309}, {"id": 190751, "content": "下机的时候根本挤不到过道里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878322}, {"id": 190496, "content": "两个小时的飞机硬是座了8个小时才到", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593935}, {"id": 191520, "content": "经历了头等舱的餐食，再坐经济舱我表示只喝水就好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281513}]}